Specify the Frequency Excursion Threshold. It is the ratio of the core frequency. Pcode Clips betwen Pm and P01.

0 < X < 17 unit is 2.3 * power(2, TW) ms and (2^17 ms = ~302 seconds) X is clipped to betwen 0 and 17. Time windows may become inaccurate for TW < 5. Valid TW range is 0 to 17. I.e. Max time window is about 302 seconds.
For SPR it's currently 0. New feature version come in the future will need to uprev this.
0x0 (Default)=Inband interface for PEM is enabled. 0x1=OOB interface for PEM is enabled.
0 (Default): Disable PEM. 1: Enable PEM
